  <div id="R34PHLIU4E5655" class="a-section review"><div class="a-row helpful-votes-count"><span class="a-size-small a-color-secondary review-votes">77
      of 80
      people found the following review helpful
  </span></div><div class="a-row"><a class="a-link-normal" href="/gp/review/R34PHLIU4E5655/ref=cm_cr_pr_rvw_ttl?ASIN=B000065DJY"><i class="a-icon a-icon-star a-star-5 review-rating"></i></a><span class="a-letter-space"></span><a class="a-link-normal review-title a-color-base a-text-normal a-text-bold" href="/gp/review/R34PHLIU4E5655/ref=cm_cr_pr_rvw_ttl?ASIN=B000065DJY">The best!</a></div><div class="a-row"><span class="review-byline"><span class="a-color-secondary">By </span><a class="a-link-normal" href="/gp/pdp/profile/AYW1PP8IMSXOF/ref=cm_cr_pr_pdp">Amazon Customer</a></span><span class="a-declarative" data-action="cr-popup" data-cr-popup="{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Help&quot;,&quot;height&quot;:&quot;340&quot;,&quot;width&quot;:&quot;340&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;/gp/help/customer/display.html/ref=cm_cr_dp_bdg_help?ie=UTF8&amp;nodeId=14279681&amp;pop-up=1#tr&quot;}"></span><span class="a-letter-space"></span><span class="a-color-secondary review-date">on Thu Oct 02 14:06:28 UTC 2003</span></div><div class="a-row a-spacing-top-mini review-data"><div class="a-section">



  I always look for a hair dryer that has separate heat and air flow settings, and a removable filter.  This has those features.  I had been curious about the ionic feature and when my conair died, I decided I'd purchase one with an ionic feature -afterall, it was only about 5 bucks more?  I was skeptical enough to keep all the packaging in order to return it if it didn't work.  Afterall, who needs a dryer that doesn't work?  I didn't have to return this one.<br />Have you ever left your hair in a towel until it was completely dry?  That is how your hair will feel when you use this dryer, only it will take a much shorter amount of time.  And be styled the way you want it to be!<br />I've found that this dryer does dry faster, and leaves my hair softer and shinier and fuller than my old conair.<br />I've got long thin hair, so thin that it NEVER keeps a curl, or the body and fullness that is there when you first dry it.  This dryer allows my hair to keep body and fullness throughout the day.<br />I'm not sure about other ionic dryers, but this one has a switch to turn off the ionic feature if you'd like - although I can't imagine why.<br />I would highly recommend this hair dryer.
